@startuml UC-01_Registration_Login_Sequence

title UC-01: User Registration & Login - Sequence Diagram

skinparam SequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam SequenceArrowColor #0277BD
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam ActorBorderColor #1976D2
skinparam ActorFontColor #0D47A1
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #0277BD
skinparam ParticipantFontColor #01579B
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam SequenceGroupBackgroundColor #FFF9C4

actor User
participant Frontend
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant FirebaseService
participant "Firebase Auth" as FirebaseAuth
participant Database as DB
participant NotificationService
participant EmailService

note over User, EmailService: Registration Flow

User -> Frontend: 1. Click Register / Enter Email & Password
Frontend -> API: 2. POST /api/v1/auth/register
API -> FirebaseService: 3. create_user(email, password, name)

FirebaseService -> FirebaseAuth: 4. Create Firebase User Account
activate FirebaseAuth
FirebaseAuth --> FirebaseService: 5. Return uid + id_token
deactivate FirebaseAuth

FirebaseService -> DB: 6. Store User Profile
activate DB
DB --> FirebaseService: 7. Confirm Storage
deactivate DB

FirebaseService -> NotificationService: 8. Queue Email Verification
NotificationService -> EmailService: 9. Send Verification Email
activate EmailService
EmailService --> NotificationService: 10. Email Sent
deactivate EmailService

FirebaseService --> API: 11. Return {uid, token, message}
API --> Frontend: 12. 201 Created + Auth Token
Frontend --> User: 13. Show Success + Redirect to Email Verification

note over User, EmailService: Email Verification

User -> EmailService: 14. Click Verification Link
EmailService -> API: 15. GET /api/v1/auth/verify-email?token=X
API -> FirebaseService: 16. verify_email_token(token)
FirebaseService -> FirebaseAuth: 17. Mark Email as Verified
FirebaseAuth --> FirebaseService: 18. Confirmed
FirebaseService -> DB: 19. Update User.emailVerified = true
DB --> FirebaseService: 20. Updated
FirebaseService --> API: 21. Verified
API --> EmailService: 22. Success Response
EmailService --> User: 23. Email Verified + Redirect to Login

note over User, EmailService: Login Flow

User -> Frontend: 24. Click Login / Enter Email & Password
Frontend -> API: 25. POST /api/v1/auth/login
API -> FirebaseService: 26. authenticate_user(email, password)

FirebaseService -> FirebaseAuth: 27. Sign In User
activate FirebaseAuth
FirebaseAuth --> FirebaseService: 28. Return id_token
deactivate FirebaseAuth

FirebaseService -> DB: 29. Fetch User Profile
activate DB
DB --> FirebaseService: 30. Return User Data
deactivate DB

FirebaseService -> NotificationService: 31. Log Login Event
NotificationService -> DB: 32. Track Analytics Event
DB --> NotificationService: 33. Event Logged

FirebaseService --> API: 34. Return {uid, token, user}
API --> Frontend: 35. 200 OK + Auth Token + User Data
Frontend --> User: 36. Store Token + Redirect to Dashboard

note over User, EmailService: Forgot Password Flow

User -> Frontend: 37. Click "Forgot Password"
Frontend -> API: 38. POST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password
API -> FirebaseService: 39. send_password_reset(email)

FirebaseService -> FirebaseAuth: 40. Generate Reset Link
FirebaseAuth -> EmailService: 41. Send Password Reset Email
activate EmailService
EmailService --> FirebaseAuth: 42. Email Sent
deactivate EmailService

FirebaseService --> API: 43. OK
API --> Frontend: 44. Show Confirmation Message
Frontend --> User: 45. "Check Your Email for Reset Link"

User -> EmailService: 46. Click Reset Link
EmailService -> Frontend: 47. Navigate to Reset Password Form
Frontend -> User: 48. Enter New Password
User -> API: 49. POST /api/v1/auth/reset-password
API -> FirebaseService: 50. reset_password(token, new_password)
FirebaseService -> FirebaseAuth: 51. Update Password
FirebaseAuth --> FirebaseService: 52. Password Updated
FirebaseService --> API: 53. Success
API --> Frontend: 54. Password Reset Successful
Frontend --> User: 55. Redirect to Login

@enduml
